{"tid":664632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"赴劉霞寓所探望　歐5外交官遭警攔截","createTime":"2018-05-14T08:44:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T10:25:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"19d346560b8a981625239683cbcb9e57fc9a883e","tid":664632,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T08:44:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180514/20390313\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180514%2F20390313&d=jP1xHi%2F8I8lBzWYhOTrsJzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=aba73ae2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180514%2F20390313&h=500ea8ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180514/20390313</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月14日 <br />\n<br />\n赴劉霞寓所探望　歐5外交官遭警攔截<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180514/large/a1405a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180514%2Flarge%2Fa1405a.gif&h=e6005489&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■劉曉波逝世將近一年，劉霞一直被禁錮北京家中，且被禁止出國。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n已故諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波遺孀劉霞被中共軟禁7年多，從未被起訴或定罪，身心受頑疾折磨，曾哭訴會「以死抗爭」，只能繼續叫天不應，叫地不聞。日前5名歐洲外交官前往其寓所探望，但在大門外被中方人員阻止，擋在大門外。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者多次探訪屢遭截<br />\n<br />\n法新社昨天報道，包括法國、德國及歐盟的5名歐洲外交官，上周五（11日）早上探望劉霞，卻在劉霞寓所樓下被警衞截停，檢查證件後，拒絕他們進入大廈，也沒有解釋禁止探望劉霞的理由。<br />\n<br />\n自2010年劉曉波獲得諾貝爾和平獎後，劉霞開始被中共軟禁，當局變本加厲，劉曉波逝世將近一年，劉霞一直被禁錮北京家中，被禁止出國，但中國官方卻不斷重複強調「劉霞擁有行動自由」。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指，法新社記者近年多次嘗試探訪劉霞，但每次都在其寓所樓下被便衣男子阻止。<br />\n<br />\n月初，流亡海外的中國異見作家廖亦武公佈與劉霞的電話錄音，可以聽到劉霞激動痛哭，其後又向廖亦武表示沒有留戀，「以死抗爭對於我，最簡單不過」。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/Twitter  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n陸艦主動打招呼　稱台艦軍官慌亂應對<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n食世界第四辣「魔鬼辣椒」　嗜辣男「瀕死」向警察求救"},{"pid":"45591993b90a3f64ca858a76efac9910b3691758","tid":664632,"uid":92376,"like":7,"dislike":17,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T08:45:37.000Z","msg":"食世界第四辣「魔鬼辣椒」　嗜辣男「瀕死」向警察求救<br />\n<br />\n貼呢篇OK?"},{"pid":"8a49754843f248a58ad223326b175fd14287223c","tid":664632,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T09:04:41.000Z","msg":"歐盟廢到呢"},{"pid":"56101a2591e06fe2b7ef0dfee38b24c2e403cf7a","tid":664632,"uid":88250,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"45591993b90a3f64ca858a76efac9910b3691758","tid":664632,"uid":92376,"like":7,"dislike":17,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T08:45:37.000Z","msg":"食世界第四辣「魔鬼辣椒」　嗜辣男「瀕死」向警察求救<br />\n<br />\n貼呢篇OK?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T01:05:25.000Z","msg":"是次發文的$0.5獎金已發到閣下帳戶, 請知悉"},{"pid":"383591445b0a303b6e0afe6b03d9d34a241bcd66","tid":664632,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"56101a2591e06fe2b7ef0dfee38b24c2e403cf7a","tid":664632,"uid":88250,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"45591993b90a3f64ca858a76efac9910b3691758","tid":664632,"uid":92376,"like":7,"dislike":17,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T08:45:37.000Z","msg":"食世界第四辣「魔鬼辣椒」　嗜辣男「瀕死」向警察求救<br />\n<br />\n貼呢篇OK?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T01:05:25.000Z","msg":"是次發文的$0.5獎金已發到閣下帳戶, 請知悉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T01:06:47.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9290ada1f59d410e578f134f820f43651b146de7","tid":664632,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T01:13:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e016647a6d117ca309beb1ee229f7b65a2d8043d","tid":664632,"uid":31637,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T01:16:03.000Z","msg":"Ff 習近平係明君果班，會唔會又ff 係江派做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aeb620f4f5b7b96f01d510ef2c6cb52038c40a1","tid":664632,"uid":21917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e016647a6d117ca309